                    width="100px">
                <!--text below has padding added via bootstrap for spacing above it-->
                <p class="pt-4">All your sporting needs in one location. If we don't have it, then you dont need it!!
                </p>
                <p> Shop with us to guarantee you<br>
                    <em>Score Your Next Victory</em>
                </p>

            </div>
            <!--List of features items with link to the store page sections, bootstrap for spacing and padded bottom of 2 before the list-->
